254
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:26,010
It could be considered avenging the hundreds of dead souls in Carefree Valley.

255
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:33,590
This was the antidote my father created.

256
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:38,410
It can temporarily weaken the power of the Force Eaters.

257
00:27:39,340 --> 00:27:41,370
Maybe it can help you.

258
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:47,700
Su Tang, I promise you.

259
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,910
I will completely destroy the Mountain and Sea Gang.

260
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:57,589
- Master.
- Master Chu Min.

261
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:17,750
Who are you?

262
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:20,509
Master, I'm Su Tang.

263
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,260
What's wrong?

264
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:30,530
She was bitten by the blood snakes.

265
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:34,250
Liu Song also imposed the Pneuma of Essence on her repeatedly.

266
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:37,600
She may have lost her memory.

267
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,140
Then, what do we do?

268
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:48,400
Senior Brother, since Master has woken up.

269
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:51,110
I'll take her and go.

270
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,700
Where are you going?

271
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,990
Right now, I'm afraid only one person can save us.

272
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:00,590
I'm going to go find him.

273
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:05,250
You mean Lu Ping?

274
00:31:06,020 --> 00:31:07,720
You are awake?

275
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:14,680
You woke up at just the right time.

276
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:18,630
This is when the sunshine is the warmest. Flowers bloom better.

277
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:21,139
Smell them. Don't they smell good?

278
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:29,200
What's wrong? Still groggy from sleeping?

279
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:32,430
Where… Where am I?

280
00:31:33,620 --> 00:31:36,240
In a small village under Big Dipper.

281
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:40,590
During the peace talks in E'zhou, my brother and I passed by here.

282
00:31:40,590 --> 00:31:44,700
I saw it was beautiful here, there were so many flowers.

283
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:49,560
I knew how you'd always talk about going home to plant flowers.

284
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:53,680
That was when I decided that if I had the chance, I'd bring you here.

285
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:56,479
How is it? Do you like it?

286
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:58,980
Yes.

287
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,680
I like it very much.

288
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:11,940
Do you like the flowers here or the person here?

289
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:16,250
Of course, I like the person more.

290
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,630
I like you, too.

291
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,910
My food is still cooking!

292
00:32:30,910 --> 00:32:32,950
You know how to cook, too?

293
