294
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:47,080
Miss Qin, you don't have any luck with cooking.

295
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,940
This is the third time I've failed already.

296
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:53,720
If I fail this time, we won't have any rice left.

297
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:57,280
It doesn't matter. We can eat this.

298
00:32:57,280 --> 00:33:00,440
Do you hate what I cooked that much?

299
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,140
Silly girl.

300
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,890
I don't have much longer to hate you.

301
00:33:12,040 --> 00:33:13,840
I can't be saved.

302
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,560
Isn't that right?

303
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:25,919
That's right, there's no way to save you.

304
00:33:25,919 --> 00:33:27,680
But instead of waiting for death sadly…

305
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:30,210
...why not live happily for the rest of these days.

306
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:34,890
I'll cook tomorrow.

307
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:39,830
How about marrying me tonight?

308
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:47,170
