312
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:11,710
The heavens witness.

313
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:14,330
The moon knows the heart.

314
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:18,860
Today, I, Lu Ping, am fortunate to have Qin Sang as my wife.

315
00:35:18,860 --> 00:35:20,780
I don't wish to be with her until we're old.

316
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:24,560
I only ask for one morning and one night.

317
00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:26,260
The earth is a witness.

318
00:35:26,260 --> 00:35:28,360
The flowers understand our hopes.

319
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:31,740
Today, I, Qin Sang, am fortunate to have Lu Ping as my husband.

320
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:35,520
I don't envy immortal couples. I just want to be together.

